  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large skillet over medium heat and add a splash of oil.",
    "Add minced garlic, grated ginger, and sliced shallot, saut\u00e9ing until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Stir in red curry paste, cooking for another 30 seconds until the aroma releases.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and stir to combine, letting the mixture come to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add the peeled king prawns and cook for 3-4 minutes until they turn pink and opaque.",
    "Season with fish sauce, lime juice, and sugar, adjusting to taste for balance of saltiness and sweetness.",
    "Fold in torn kaffir lime leaves and torn Thai basil leaves, cooking for an additional minute.",
    "Remove from heat, garnish with fresh coriander, and serve immediately with steamed rice if desired."
  ],
